Author: orthofuckyrself
Text: I know. And it is the miscalculation.   But I know it is beyond lol, because I know I'm in a surplus :p   But it's less than half a pound. A blip. The important thing is to maintain a healthy mindset. If I have to cut a little sooner, then I'll do that.

Author: SemicolonButterfly
Text: Miscalculation can have an emotional weight totally out of proportion to physical ramifications.  1500 cal is less than half a pound and that would have go be eaten *beyond* maintenance.  Take a deep breath. And then another.
